---

<section id="bridal-party" class="pt-12 pb-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-wedding-raspberry/5 via-wedding-dark-matcha-green/5 to-wedding-raspberry/5">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-brush text-center text-wedding-dark-matcha-green mb-4">
      Our A-Team
    </h2>
    <p class="text-center text-gray-700 mb-12 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      The incredible people who have been by our side through it all. We're so grateful to have them standing with us on our special day.
    </p>

    <!-- Bridal Party Grid -->
    <div class="space-y-12">
      <!-- Bride's Side -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-handwriting font-bold text-wedding-raspberry text-center mb-8">
          Bride's Side
        </h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">
          <!-- Maid of Honor -->
          <div class="bg-wedding-oatmilk rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg border-2 border-wedding-raspberry/20 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="text-center mb-4">
              <div class="relative w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-wedding-raspberry/30 shadow-md">
                <img
                  src="/images/bridal-party/maid-of-honor.jpg"
                  alt="Maid of Honor"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-handwriting font-bold text-wedding-raspberry mb-1">
                [Maid of Honor Name]
              </h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-wedding-raspberry font-semibold mb-3">
                Maid of Honor
              </p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-center italic">
              Our long-time travel buddy and best secret keeper since high school. She's been there for every milestone and we couldn't imagine this day without her.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Bridesmaid 1 -->
          <div class="bg-wedding-oatmilk rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg border-2 border-wedding-raspberry/20 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="text-center mb-4">
              <div class="relative w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-wedding-raspberry/30 shadow-md">
                <img
                  src="/images/bridal-party/bridesmaid-1.jpg"
                  alt="Bridesmaid"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-handwriting font-bold text-wedding-raspberry mb-1">
                [Bridesmaid Name]
              </h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-wedding-raspberry font-semibold mb-3">
                Bridesmaid
              </p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-center italic">
              The friend who always knows how to make us laugh and brings the best energy to every gathering. Her support means the world to us.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Bridesmaid 2 -->
          <div class="bg-wedding-oatmilk rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg border-2 border-wedding-raspberry/20 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="text-center mb-4">
              <div class="relative w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-wedding-raspberry/30 shadow-md">
                <img
                  src="/images/bridal-party/bridesmaid-2.jpg"
                  alt="Bridesmaid"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-handwriting font-bold text-wedding-raspberry mb-1">
                [Bridesmaid Name]
              </h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-wedding-raspberry font-semibold mb-3">
                Bridesmaid
              </p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-center italic">
              A true friend who's been there through thick and thin. Her wisdom and kindness have been a constant source of strength.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Groom's Side -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-handwriting font-bold text-wedding-dark-matcha-green text-center mb-8">
          Groom's Side
        </h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">
          <!-- Best Man -->
          <div class="bg-wedding-oatmilk rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg border-2 border-wedding-dark-matcha-green/20 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="text-center mb-4">
              <div class="relative w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-wedding-dark-matcha-green/30 shadow-md">
                <img
                  src="/images/bridal-party/best-man.jpg"
                  alt="Best Man"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-handwriting font-bold text-wedding-dark-matcha-green mb-1">
                [Best Man Name]
              </h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-wedding-dark-matcha-green font-semibold mb-3">
                Best Man
              </p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-center italic">
              The brother I never had. From childhood adventures to adult life, he's been my rock and my partner in crime. Couldn't ask for a better best man.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Groomsman 1 -->
          <div class="bg-wedding-oatmilk rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg border-2 border-wedding-dark-matcha-green/20 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="text-center mb-4">
              <div class="relative w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-wedding-dark-matcha-green/30 shadow-md">
                <img
                  src="/images/bridal-party/groomsman-1.jpg"
                  alt="Groomsman"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-handwriting font-bold text-wedding-dark-matcha-green mb-1">
                [Groomsman Name]
              </h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-wedding-dark-matcha-green font-semibold mb-3">
                Groomsman
              </p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-center italic">
              A loyal friend who's always up for an adventure. His positive energy and unwavering support have made all the difference.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Groomsman 2 -->
          <div class="bg-wedding-oatmilk rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg border-2 border-wedding-dark-matcha-green/20 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="text-center mb-4">
              <div class="relative w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-wedding-dark-matcha-green/30 shadow-md">
                <img
                  src="/images/bridal-party/groomsman-2.jpg"
                  alt="Groomsman"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-handwriting font-bold text-wedding-dark-matcha-green mb-1">
                [Groomsman Name]
              </h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-wedding-dark-matcha-green font-semibold mb-3">
                Groomsman
              </p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-center italic">
              The friend who brings out the best in everyone around him. His humor and genuine care for others make him an irreplaceable part of our lives.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

